title: DDFP 405: Week 11 preview & Terence Newman
itunes:title: DDFP 405: Week 11 preview & Terence Newman
description:
Shek is joined by Handsome Hank and Patrick Claybon to make their Week 11 "Red Challenge Flag" picks. Plus, Shek introduces the next installment of "Mascot Matchups," in which a Miami Dolphin duels with a Dallas Cowboy. Lastly, Shek and Handsome Hank speak with Minnesota Vikings cornerback Terence Newman about his 2003 Dallas Cowboys teammates, Teddy Bridgewater and being named NFC Defensive Player of the Week.

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com
